List available detection rules

Usage: aur-scan rules [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -s, --severity <SEVERITY>  Show only rules of this severity [possible values: critical, high, medium, low, info]
  -d, --details              Show rule details
  -c, --config <CONFIG>      Configuration file path
  -v, --verbose              Enable verbose output
  -q, --quiet                Quiet mode (only show findings)
  -h, --help                 Print help
